sentences.english: There was no significant difference in self- concept between two sub -groups with different age in left -behind children.
sentences.chinese: 不同年齡組留守兒童的自我意識比較無顯著性差異。

sentences.english: In male and female, the peak age of death started at 30 years group.
sentences.chinese: 死亡高峯年齡男女性均始於30～歲年齡組。

sentences.english: In 2009, that was true of almost half in that age group.
sentences.chinese: 在2009年，同樣的年齡組中幾乎有一半人未婚。

sentences.english: TG levels increased along with the increasing of age but HDL-C levels decreased.
sentences.chinese: 個別年齡組男女兒童間血脂水平有差別。

sentences.english: Certain age groups will be balloted at this time.
sentences.chinese: 這次對某年齡組的人徵募。

sentences.english: All age groups and all regions are affected by NCDs.
sentences.chinese: 所有年齡組以及所有區域都受到非傳染性疾病的影響。

sentences.english: These causes account for nearly 80% of deaths in this age group.
sentences.chinese: 這一年齡組死亡的約80%由這些原因導致。

sentences.english: Across all age groups and regions, both genders are at risk of falls.
sentences.chinese: 在所有年齡組和地區，男女都有跌傷的風險。

sentences.english: Then, age sets in. The warning signs come in brittle bones and weakened muscles.
sentences.chinese: 然後，個年齡組的警告標誌來脆骨頭和肌肉削弱。

sentences.english: Classes in all subject areas except social studies are mixed-grade groupings .
sentences.chinese: 除了社會科學外，班級在所有學科都是混合年齡組的。

sentences.english: Is this game meant for a specific age-group?
sentences.chinese: 這種遊戲是專爲特定年齡組的人設計的嗎？

sentences.english: The percentage of males increased with each age group.
sentences.chinese: 每個年齡組的男性比例有所增加。

sentences.english: Lassa fever occurs in all age groups and in both men and women.
sentences.chinese: 拉沙熱發生在所有年齡組的男女中間。

sentences.english: Observed age-group differences were very small, however.
sentences.chinese: 但是觀察年齡組之間的差異很小。

sentences.english: The brief dictated that Spore had no specific target age-group.
sentences.chinese: 在簡短的決定了孢子並沒有特定的目標年齡組。
